SURVEILLANCE DICTIONARY (02)
============================
[see
Surveillance dictionary: RFI 970409170754]
[1]
Date: Wed, 9 Apr 1997
From: Luiz Jacintho da Silva <luisjs@correionet.com.br>

I would suggest Control of Communicable Diseases Manual, 16th
ed.,Benenson,A.S.(ed), American Public Health Association, 1995. It is low
cost and easily understandable.
American Public Health Association
1015 Fifteenth St., NW
Washington, DC 20005
USA
